snippet.title: One Show Only Release Trailer
snippet.description:
One Show Only is a detective game where you interrogate witnesses  to a crime by playing a card game against them.

The game is available for purchase on PC/Mac here:
https://tristandahl.itch.io/oneshowonly

And this is the website:
http://www.tristandahl.co.za/oneshowonly.html
